# Privacy Policy for WallIt

Last updated: April 14, 2025

## Introduction

Thank you for choosing to use WallIt. We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your information is collected, used, and disclosed by WallIt.

## Information We Collect

WallIt is designed to be privacy-friendly and collects minimal data:

- **Storage Access**: We request access to your device's storage only to save wallpapers when you choose to download them.
- **Usage Data**: Anonymous usage statistics may be collected to help us improve the app.

## How We Use Information

We use the information we collect to:
- Provide and maintain our Service
- Allow you to save wallpapers to your device
- Improve our application

## Third-Party Services

Our app uses images from Unsplash, which are provided under the Unsplash License. We do not share your personal information with Unsplash or other third parties.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
